Package: universalaccel
Type: Package
Title: Universal Accelerometer Summary Metrics
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person("Jimmy Duhamahoro", email = "jduhamah@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A fully reproducible workflow for importing and autocalibrating raw accelerometer data from ActiGraph, Axivity, and GENEActiv devices. 
             The package computes MIMS, Activity Index (AI), ENMO, MAD, ROCAM, and ActiGraph activity counts, with optional Choi nonâ€‘wear classification. 
             It also provides a downstream analysis pipeline for interpreting daily intensity distributions using NHANES population references.
